title: New York City Council Districts
name: New York City Council Districts
description: The City Council Districts of New York City clipped to the shoreline at mean high tide.  The City Council Districts are the result of the recent redistricting process, which takes place every ten years to reflect population changes reported in the 2000 Census. These geographies were redrawn by the New York City Council Redistricting Commission.
